revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Floor_TransferTrigger}} {{Special|235|tag|Floor|TransferTrigger}} * ''tag'': Tag of affected sector
Transfers the floor picture and sector special from one sector to another.
The source sector is chosen by looking at the sector on Side 1 of the triggered linedef.
== Examples ==
{{noexamples}}
== Conversions from linedef types == The following Doom map format types can be converted as : {| {{prettytable}} !Type!!Conversion!!Trigger |- |{{icon|Boom}} 153:W1 Change Floor Texture & Effect (Trigger Model) || Floor_TransferTrigger (tag) || Player Cross |- |{{icon|Boom}} 154:WR Change Floor Texture & Effect (Trigger Model) || Floor_TransferTrigger (tag) || Player Cross, Repeatable |- |{{icon|Boom}} 189:S1 Change Floor Texture & Effect (Trigger Model) || Floor_TransferTrigger (tag) || Player Use |- |{{icon|Boom}} 190:SR Change Floor Texture & Effect (Trigger Model) || Floor_TransferTrigger (tag) || Player Use, Repeatable |}
